  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Monster End is a top-down dual joystick shooting light ROGUE game where players take on the role of a post apocalyptic survivor and defeat hordes of monsters. Choose from props and weapons with unique features, create unique character attributes, and survive until you escape danger. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> During the game, you must constantly strengthen yourself</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Gameplay </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You need to constantly defeat enemies rushing towards you, absorb experience balls after defeating enemies to increase your level, and choose the most suitable one among many enhancements (as the level increases, the ability enhancement will also become stronger)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/9639066e8a09f2bb172d21174ec05fd4.poster.avif?t=1741232289\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/9639066e8a09f2bb172d21174ec05fd4.webm?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/9639066e8a09f2bb172d21174ec05fd4.mp4?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Open the treasure chest </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In the map, the treasure chest will refresh and contain powerful items and equipment. You can equip weapons through the treasure chest or use items in the treasure chest. More suitable weapons can make your character stronger</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/86b2dbef6cee2cd3c00f6dbaa8e5a84f.poster.avif?t=1741232289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/86b2dbef6cee2cd3c00f6dbaa8e5a84f.webm?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/86b2dbef6cee2cd3c00f6dbaa8e5a84f.mp4?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Attribute details </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>According to the button prompt, you can view your attribute details, which include basic attributes and skill attributes, and can be viewed during pause</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/ffb373b6fd0fe996ae3d20c6c6d75f11.poster.avif?t=1741232289\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/ffb373b6fd0fe996ae3d20c6c6d75f11.webm?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/ffb373b6fd0fe996ae3d20c6c6d75f11.mp4?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Vending machine </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The game will refresh the vending machine every once in a while. After entering the vending machine, players can spend coins to purchase items, weapons, and attributes. The goods will be given to the player after leaving the vending machine. If the coins are insufficient, the goods can be locked and purchased again next time. The price of the vending machine will continue to increase over time</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/8c38c10a9dbdeff7b93d0bc0306f2ed3.poster.avif?t=1741232289\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/8c38c10a9dbdeff7b93d0bc0306f2ed3.webm?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/8c38c10a9dbdeff7b93d0bc0306f2ed3.mp4?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Pick up ground items </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Items can be discarded or picked up, and they will disappear after being stored on the ground for a period of time</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/ab32f408d42989e82eabb2a455f77b23.poster.avif?t=1741232289\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/ab32f408d42989e82eabb2a455f77b23.webm?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/ab32f408d42989e82eabb2a455f77b23.mp4?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Heavenly Official Blessing </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>After defeating some elites, the Heavenly Official Blessing will be activated. In the Heavenly Official Blessing, players can choose a powerful enhancement to help them improve better. The higher the level of the Heavenly Official Blessing, the stronger the rewards obtained</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/a37804fcf8a7f54c29b9b85bce4b2561.poster.avif?t=1741232289\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/a37804fcf8a7f54c29b9b85bce4b2561.webm?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/a37804fcf8a7f54c29b9b85bce4b2561.mp4?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Weapon Upgrade </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Except for non upgradable weapons, most weapons can be upgraded, with a maximum level of 8 stars. When opening a treasure chest or store, similar weapons will appear, and they will be upgraded after picking up or purchasing. Weapons with higher star ratings will provide more significant effects</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/04daa762cb8b62d10f4707eaf08d0506.poster.avif?t=1741232289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/04daa762cb8b62d10f4707eaf08d0506.webm?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/04daa762cb8b62d10f4707eaf08d0506.mp4?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Infinite Enhancement </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>After each game, the character will gain experience to level up. The higher the level, the more attributes will be provided, and there is no upper limit to this level. Higher levels can help you survive better</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/0bbe8f85d5581974eb844e4c2aa0fc0f.poster.avif?t=1741232289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/0bbe8f85d5581974eb844e4c2aa0fc0f.webm?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461220/extras/0bbe8f85d5581974eb844e4c2aa0fc0f.mp4?t=1741232289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p>",
